@page "/sources"

<PageTitle>Data Sources | GameMarketIntel</PageTitle>

<section class="page-heading">
    <span class="page-heading__eyebrow"> Research foundation </span>

    <h1>Data Sources</h1>

    <p class="page-heading__description">
        Review the sources that support the GameMarketIntel dataset and
        the context used to evaluate their reliability.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="source-introduction">
    <div class="source-introduction__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <ellipse cx="12" cy="6" rx="7.5" ry="3" />
            <path d="M4.5 6v6c0 1.7 3.4 3 7.5 3s7.5-1.3 7.5-3V6" />
            <path d="M4.5 12v6c0 1.7 3.4 3 7.5 3s7.5-1.3 7.5-3v-6" />
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2>Source catalog integration is coming next</h2>

        <p>
            The backend already exposes source information. This page will
            receive the complete source catalog after the Comparable Games
            read experience is established.
        </p>

        <p>
            Until then, the current frontend milestone remains focused on
            searching and reviewing comparable games.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<a class="button button--primary" href="/games">
    Go to Comparable Games

    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5 12h14M14 7l5 5-5 5" />
    </svg>
</a>